  body "hadsanid}}\n* Sorbian:\n*: Lower Sorbian: {{tt|dsb|źěkujom se}}\n*: Upper Sorbian: {{tt|hsb|dźakuju so}}\n* Sotho: {{tt|st|kea leboha}}\n* Spanish: {{tt+|es|gracias}}, {{tt+|es|muchas gracias}}\n* Sun"
  body "danese: {{tt+|su|nuhun}}, {{tt|su|hatur nuhun}}\n* Surigaonon: {{t|sgd|salamat}}\n* Svan: {{tt|sva|ივასუ ხარი}}\n* Swahili: {{tt+|sw|asante}}, {{tt+|sw|shukrani}}\n* Swedish: {{tt+|sv|tack}}, {{tt+|sv"
  body "|tack så mycket}}\n* Sylheti: {{tt|syl|ꠗꠁꠘ꠆ꠘꠛꠣꠖ}}\n* Tagalog: {{tt+|tl|salamat}}\n* Tahitian: {{tt|ty|māuruuru}}\n* Tajik: {{tt+|tg|ташаккур}}, {{tt|tg|раҳмат}}, {{tt|tg|сипос}}, {{t+|tg|мамнун|alt=ма"
