  body "{""parse"":{""title"":""thanks"",""pageid"":33788,""redirects"":[],""wikitext"":""==English==\n\n===Alternative forms===\n* {{alt|en|t'anks|thanx|thx|tnx|10x|fanks||all|_|nonstandard}}\n\n===Etymology===\n{{ety|en"
  body "|:inh|enm:thanks<ety:inh<ang:þanc<alt:þancas>>>}}\nFrom {{inh|en|enm|thanks}}, {{m|enm|thankes}}, from {{inh|en|ang|þancas|t=thanks}}, from {{inh|en|gem-pro|*þankōs}}, nominative plural of {{m|gem-pro"
  body "|*þankaz||thought, gratitude}}, from {{der|en|ine-pro|*teng-||to think, feel}}. More at {{l|en|thank}}.\n\n===Pronunciation===\n* {{a|en|non-æ-raising}}\n** {{IPA|en|/ˈθæŋks/|[ˈθæŋks]}}\n*** {{a|en|th"
  body "-fronting}}\n**** {{IPA|en|/ˈfæŋks/|[ˈfæŋks]|a=UK}}\n** {{IPA|en|/ˈðæŋks/|[ˈðæŋks]}}\n* {{a|en|æ-raising}}\n** {{a|en|US|CA}}\n*** {{IPA|en|/ˈθeɪ̯ŋks/|[ˈθeɪ̯ŋks]|~|/ˈθɛ̃ŋks/|[ˈθɛ̃ŋks]}}\n**** {{audio|"
  body "en|en-us-thanks.ogg|a=US}}\n*** {{IPA|en|/ˈðeɪ̯ŋks/|[ˈðeɪ̯ŋks]|~|/ˈðɛ̃ŋks/|[ˈðɛ̃ŋks]}}\n* {{rhymes|en|æŋks|s=1}}\n* {{hyph|en|thanks}}\n\n===Interjection===\n{{en-intj}}\n\n# {{non-gloss|Used to expre"
  body "ss [[appreciation]] or [[gratitude]].}}\n#: {{syn|en|Thesaurus:thank you}}\n#: {{ux|en|Could you give me a hand, please?'' — Yes, sure. — '''''Thanks'''. —Have you got enough now? —Yes, '''thanks'''.}"
  body "}\n#: {{ux|en|Would you like some potatoes? — '''Thanks'''. —How many?}}\n#* {{RQ:Shakespeare Midsummer|5|1|passage='''Thanks,''' courteous wall: Jove shield thee well for this!}}\n\n====Derived terms"
  body "====\n{{col|en|thankies|thanksgive|thanksgiver|thanksgiving|thanksies|thanks a lot|many thanks|no thanks|no thanks to|thanks a bunch|thanks a heap|thanks a million|thanks a ton|thanks be|thanks for co"
  body "ming|thanks in advance|vote of thanks|thanks, but no thanks|thanks for asking|thanks for nothing|thanks for your help|thanks for coming to my TED Talk}}\n\n====Translations====\n{{trans-top|used to ex"
