  body "|wyi|ngoon godjin}}\n{{trans-bottom}}\n\n===Noun===\n{{en-noun|p|sg=thank<l:obsolete>}}\n\n# {{senseid|en|expression of gratitude}} An [[expression]] of [[appreciation]] or [[gratitude]].\n#: {{ux|en|"
  body "After all I’ve done, a simple acknowledgment is the '''thanks''' I get?}}\n# [[grateful|Grateful]] [[feeling#Noun|feelings]] or [[thought#Noun|thoughts]]; [[favor#Noun|favour]], [[goodwill]], [[gracio"
  body "usness]].\n\n===Noun===\n{{head|en|noun form}}\n\n# {{lb|en|obsolete}} {{plural of|en|thank}}\n\n====Derived terms====\n{{col|en|thanks to}}\n\n====Translations====\n{{trans-top|expression of gratitud"
  body "e}}\n* American Sign Language: {{t|ase|OpenB@Chin-PalmBack OpenB@FromChin-PalmUp}}\n* Bengali: {{t+|bn|ধন্যবাদ}}, {{t+|bn|শুকরিয়া}}\n* Bulgarian: {{t+|bg|призна́телност|m}}, {{t+|bg|благода́рност}}\n"
  body "* Catalan: {{t+|ca|mercè|f}}, {{t+|ca|mercès|f}}, {{t+|ca|gràcies|f-p}}\n* Chinese:\n*: Hokkien: {{t+|nan-hbl|多謝|tr=to-siā / to-siǎ / to͘-siā}}\n* Czech: {{t+|cs|díky|m-p}}\n* Danish: {{t+|da|tak|c}}\"
  body "n* Dutch: {{t+|nl|bedankt}}\n* Esperanto: {{t|eo|danko}}\n* Ewe: {{t|ee|akpe|n}}\n* Faroese: {{t|fo|tøkk}}, {{t|fo|takk}}\n* Finnish: {{t+|fi|kiitos}}, {{t|fi|kiitokset}}\n* French: [[remerciement]]s "
  body "{{g|m-p}}\n* Galician: {{t|gl|grazas|f-p}}\n* German: {{t+|de|Dank|m}}, {{t|de|Danksagung|f}}\n* Gothic: {{t|got|𐌸𐌰𐌲𐌺𐍃|m}}\n* Greek: {{t+|el|ευχαριστώ|n}}\n* Hebrew: {{t+|he|תּוֹדָה|tr=todá}}\n* Hunga"
  body "rian: {{t+|hu|köszönet}}\n* Hunsrik: {{t|hrx|Dank|m}}\n* Icelandic: {{t+|is|þökk|f}}, {{t|is|þakkargerð|f}}, {{t|is|þakkargjörð|f}}\n* Japanese: {{t+|ja|謝辞|tr=shaji}}\n* Oromo: {{t|om|galata}}\n* Plau"
