  body "}}\n* Bulgarian: {{t+|bg|призна́телност|m}}, {{t+|bg|благода́рност}}\n* Dutch: {{t+|nl|dank|m}}\n* Finnish: {{t|fi|kiitokset|p}}\n* French: {{t+|fr|remerciement|m}}\n* German: {{t+|de|Dank|m}}\n* Gree"
