  body "k: {{t-check|sk|vďaka}}\n* Tagalog: {{t+check|tl|salamat}}\n{{trans-bottom}}\n\n===Verb===\n{{head|en|verb form}}\n\n# {{infl of|en|thank||s-verb-form}}\n\n{{cln|en|expressions of gratitude}}\n\n==Dut"
