  body "1}}\nFrom {{inh|af|nl|water}}, from {{inh|af|dum|wāter}}, from {{inh|af|odt|watar}}, from {{inh|af|gmw-pro|*watar}}, from {{inh|af|gem-pro|*watōr}}, from {{inh|af|ine-pro|*wódr̥}}.\n\n===Pronunciation"
