  body "rine]]\n# any body of water, such as a river or a lake\n# a [[disease]] where water is accumulated; [[hydrops]]\n# {{lb|af|in the plural}} a large quantity of water; [[inundation]]\n\n===Verb===\n{{af"
  body "-verb}}\n\n# to [[urinate]]\n# to [[secrete]] [[liquid]]\n\n===Derived terms===\n* {{l|af|waterbok}} \n* {{l|af|waterlemoen}}\n* {{l|af|ontwater}}\n\n===References===\n* Jan Kromhout, ''Afrikaans-Engl"
