  body "n* {{R:svenska.se|saob}}\n\n==Tocharian B==\n\n===Pronoun===\n{{head|txb|pronoun}}\n\n# [[you]] (plural), [[you all]]\n\n====See also====\n* {{l|txb|ñaś}}\n* {{l|txb|su}}\n* {{l|txb|tuwe}}\n* {{l|txb|"
